Records (see 
<tableCitation box="[308,396,829,855]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="25.[151,239,151,175]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="TABLE 1. List of species of Astiotrema (sensu stricto) Looss, 1900 we recognize followed by recorded host species and geographical distribution." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/8C906605FFC2A5184D86FF625EC8FF7B" pageId="21" pageNumber="57" tableUuid="8C906605FFC2A5184D86FF625EC8FF7B">Table 1</tableCitation>
